   <refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody ">
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">All sites must develop a formal Traffic Management Plan with suitable pedestrian/vehicle segregation.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">The plan shall include rules for safe designating parking, refueling/charging,
               repairing, and moving of disable vehicles.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">The plan shall include the provision of signs, speed limits, barriers, bollards, walk ways, etc.</li>
         </ol>
      </section>
